<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.mfat.tvhplayer</id>
  <name>TVHplayer</name>
  <summary>A desktop client for Tvheadend for watching and recording live TV channels</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0+</project_license>
  <description>
    <p>
      TVHplayer is a desktop client for Tvheadend, allowing you to watch and record TV channels from your Tvheadend server.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Watch live TV</li>
      <li>Record TV shows directly on the server</li>
      <li>Record streams locally to your computer</li>
      <li>View EPG (Electronic Program Guide) data</li>
      <li>Monitor server status and signal quality</li>
      <li>Support for multiple TVHeadend servers</li>
      <li>Cross-platform: runs on GNU/Linux, Windows and MacOS</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For more information, and instructions for setting up your own server please visit Tvheadend official website.</p>
  </description>
